  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Aged 18 years or older and fulfilling all normal criteria for blood donation

          2. Willing to be assigned to any of the study intervention groups

          3. Registered at one of the permanent donation clinics at the time of enrolment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  As the aim of the study is to be almost &quot;paper-less&quot;, it will involve remote web-based
             data collection. Hence, participants who do not have internet access and/or are not
             willing to provide an email address for study correspondence will be excluded.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
